  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "Vudnxg6RElm2YaJftz88S/DCN9g=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:35.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# five models form a hierarchy from facet through template to offering to subscription to instance\n\nThe five document models in this project form a directed graph:\n\n```\nFacet \u2500\u2500referenced-by\u2500\u2500\u2192 ResourceTemplate \u2500\u2500referenced-by\u2500\u2500\u2192 ServiceOffering\n                                                                    \u2502\n                                                          (mapOfferingToSubscription)\n                                                                    \u2193\n                                                         SubscriptionInstance\n                                                                    \u2502\n                                                           resource.id PHID\n                                                                    \u2193\n                                                          ResourceInstance\n```\n\n## Cross-Model PHID References\n\n| From | Field | To | Relationship |\n|------|-------|----|-------------|\n| ServiceOffering | `resourceTemplateId` | ResourceTemplate | \"built from this template\" |\n| ServiceOffering | `operatorId` | BuilderProfile (external) | \"offered by\" |\n| ServiceOffering | `facetBindings.facetType` | Facet | \"uses this classification\" |\n| SubscriptionInstance | `serviceOfferingId` | ServiceOffering | \"subscribed to\" |\n| SubscriptionInstance | `operatorId` | BuilderProfile (external) | \"operated by\" |\n| SubscriptionInstance | `customerId` | External | \"purchased by\" |\n| SubscriptionInstance | `resource.id` | ResourceInstance | \"has this resource\" |\n| ResourceInstance | `resourceTemplateId` | ResourceTemplate | \"based on template\" |\n| ResourceInstance | `customerId` | External | \"owned by\" |\n| ResourceTemplate | `operatorId` | BuilderProfile (external) | \"created by\" |\n| ResourceTemplate | `facetBindings.facetType` | Facet | \"uses this classification\" |\n\n## Data Flow Direction\n\n1. **Facet** defines classification options\n2. **ResourceTemplate** references Facets and defines base service catalog\n3. **ServiceOffering** references a template and adds pricing (tiers, discounts, billing cycles)\n4. **SubscriptionInstance** is initialized from an offering's final configuration via mapOfferingToSubscription\n5. **ResourceInstance** is provisioned per subscription and tracks lifecycle\n\n## Broader Ecosystem Context\n\nThese 5 local models are part of a 21-model ecosystem (see [[ecosystem map]]). Key cross-zone dependencies:\n\n- `operatorId` fields reference [[builder-profile model describes individual contributor identities]] (Organization & Identity zone)\n- SubscriptionInstance feeds into [[billing-statement model captures periodic billing summaries]] and [[invoice model generates formal payment requests]] (Finance & Reporting zones)\n- [[service-subscription model tracks service-level subscription agreements]] sits between ServiceOffering and SubscriptionInstance as the agreement layer\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[object relations]]\n- [[architecture decisions]]\n- [[ecosystem map]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:35.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:35.000Z"
    }
  },
